{
  "texts": [
    "Eighteen publications opted to use already available datasets for a total of 23 different reported datasets.",
    "Only three datasets were used by two different publications: the OSIE dataset (Xu et al., 2014), the MIT dataset (Judd et al., 2009), and the dataset from Coutrot and Guyader (2014).",
    "While the publications for the SedentaryActivity dataset (Srivastava et al., 2018) and the dataset from Greene et al. (2012) are both covered within this review.",
    "Table 1 lists all 23 datasets alongside the learning tasks that they were used for.",
    "We wanted to report these datasets because they might be available online or via correspondence with their respective authors."
  ]
}